title: Triumph-The Best of Part # 1
description:
Triumph-The Best of Part # 1 DJ Mix

This is a rip of a homemade cd that I made for use on your portable mp3 device or on you computer or
what ever you want to do with it. The Mp3 file is a single track with all song mixed together like they
do on the radio, Part # 1 is 78:13 long and contains 16 songs listed below. This was ripped from the
cd with db power amp as a single file and is 179mb in size.

Here is how it was made I use two cd decks into a mixer recorded onto a minidisc  and transfered
by tos link to a home cd recorder, all recording is done in real time. Then the cd is ripped on the computer using
dbpoweramp as a single file. All songs taken from the Remastered cd. More Triumph to come.
